## Quick Reference - Critical Rules

1. **Critical Evaluation First** - Evaluate every request before implementing
2. **Documentation is MANDATORY** - Every file, component, and function must be documented
3. **TypeScript types are MANDATORY** - No `any` types without explicit justification
4. **Server Components by default** - Only use Client Components when interactivity is required
5. **CSS Modules required** - All component styles must use CSS Modules
6. **Cloudflare Workers compatible** - All code must work in Cloudflare Workers runtime
7. **No breaking changes** - Maintain backward compatibility unless explicitly requested

